headline: CHIPOTLE CELEBRATES TOP AMERICAN ATHLETES WITH NEW LIMITED-TIME MENU ITEMS AND GOLD FOIL-WRAPPED BURRITOS

The brand will also bring back its signature gold foil across the U.S. starting February 6, available while supplies last.
